<h3>The Syntax</h3>

<h4>Selectors</h4>
<p>
A CSS ruleset starts with a <em>selector</em>. Selectors identify the element(s) that the styles will be applied to. 
</p>

<p>In this example <code>p</code> is the selector so this ruleset will apply to all paragraph elements on the page.</p>

